This folder contains some post-processing scripts that are useful for
various types of post-processing. Most of these are written to run on
a cluster such as stampede. They can be adapted for other types of
machines.

- runpp.py: run post-processors on a bunch of directories. Requires
  several scripts in simblst/

- convert_pos2txt.py: convert Gmsh data to a plaintext
  format. Requires aux_functions.py and simblst/pos2txt.geo

- aux_functions.py: auxilliary functions used by convert_pos2txt.py
